data.description: Listing price is 25k under appraisal price that was just done in August!! Come check out this spacious home. 3 bedrooms, 2 bath. Updated kitchen and appliances. Refrigerated air. Great room with wet bar. Large back yard with covered patio. Two driveways with backyard access. Park your RV, no HOA or PID. Roof has had regular maintenance recently done, along with a few windows, refrigerated air, irrigation system in backyard, as well as some plumbing and electrical repair. Come take advantage of this well-kept home with updates and a great outdoor space. Call your realtor to schedule an appointment!
